show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: When ambitious architect Aarohi is betrayed on her engagement day, a mysterious stranger offers her a new beginning — with strings attached. As secrets unravel and love clashes with deception, her journey turns into a rollercoaster of power, betrayal, and redemption.
